OL,4,Cmiles in five days for charity
OL,6,FA Navy veteran, who has hand cycled
OL,7,F321 miles in five days to raise money
OL,8,Ffor charity, was given a hero's return
OL,9,Ftoday.
OL,11,F65-year-old Paul Smith, from
OL,12,FPortsmouth, was left with life-
OL,13,Fthreatening and life-changing injuries
OL,14,Ffollowing a car crash 33 years ago
OL,15,Ftoday (2 September).
OL,17,FHe was left paralysed with locked-in
OL,18,Fsyndrome, for 12 years, and after
OL,19,Fpartially recovering, he decided to
OL,20,Fdedicate his life to fundraising.
