OL,6,FThe latest challenge saw him hand
OL,7,Fcycle from Mount Snowdon to Portsmouth.
OL,9,FIn this latest challenge, the
OL,10,FFalklands veteran has so far raised
OL,11,Fmore than #2,000, with the hopes of
OL,12,Fraising #50,000 for the Brain Tumour
OL,13,FTrust.
OL,15,FThe challenge was in memory of his
OL,16,Fgrandmother and two friends who died
OL,17,Fof the disease.
