OL,6,FHe had previously climbed Snowden on
OL,7,Fhis hands and knees, which has helped
OL,8,Fhim raise in total #2.3m for a variety
OL,9,Fof charities.
OL,11,FPaul has been taking part in charity
OL,12,Fwork for 48 years and has been
OL,13,Ftraining for over a year to complete
OL,14,Fthe challenge
OL,16,FHe says this is possibly his last
OL,17,Fmajor challenge, though he doubts he
OL,18,Fwill ever stop fundraising fully.
