OL,6,F"We are honoured that he has decided
OL,7,Fto support us with his last major
OL,8,Ffundraising challenge and wish him
OL,9,Fwell on this ambitious ride.
OL,11,F"It is sadly not uncommon to lose
OL,12,Fmultiple loved ones to the disease.
OL,13,FOne in three people know someone
OL,14,Faffected by a brain tumour, yet just
OL,15,F1% of the national spend on cancer
OL,16,Fresearch has been allocated to brain
OL,17,Ftumours since records began in 2002.
OL,19,F"Only by fundraising support like
OL,20,FPaul's can we fight back against the
OL,21,Fdisease."
